        <zone h='13000' id='17' type-v2='text' w='29400' x='50600' y='3625'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>1. Stock Trend</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Q:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> What did you observe about Nike’s stock trend?
</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>A:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Nike stock shows strong long-term growth with a peak around 2021. After that, it entered a correction phase, indicating cyclical market behavior. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone h='19000' id='18' type-v2='text' w='20100' x='75500' y='38375'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2. Moving Average Signals</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Q:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> How did you identify buy and sell signals?
</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>A:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> I used moving average crossovers where MA50 crossing above MA200 indicates a BUY signal. When MA50 crosses below MA200, it signals a SELL opportunity.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone h='9250' id='19' type-v2='text' w='40000' x='60000' y='90625'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>3. Drawdown Analysis</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Q:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> How risky is the stock?&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>A:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> The stock experiences significant drawdowns during major market events like 2008 and COVID-19. This indicates high downside risk despite long-term growth. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone h='8000' id='20' type-v2='text' w='33300' x='2700' y='92625'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Q:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Did you find any seasonal trends?
</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>A:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Yes, some months consistently show better or worse performance. This suggests potential seasonality in stock returns. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='36000' id='21' type-v2='text' w='18500' x='37000' y='65250'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>FINAL INSIGHTS</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Strong long-term growth with peak around 2021 </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Correction phase observed after peak </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Daily returns mostly stable with occasional high volatility </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Major drawdowns during market events (2008, COVID) </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Moving averages provide clear BUY/SELL signals </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Long-term investing outperforms short-term trading </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Risk management is essential for consistent returns </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
